      "description": "Hilda regenerates 2% of her max HP per second while in the bush. When entering the bush, she gains a shield equal to 15% of her max HP. After leaving the bush, the shield lasts for 5s. This effect has a 10s cooldown. Hilda's Basic Attack and Skills apply a (Wilderness Mark) on hit, which lasts up to 4s and stacks up to 6. Each stack reduces the target's Physical Defense and Magic Defense by 4%.",
