      "tips": "This is your primary source of crowd control. Movement speed is useless if you can’t pin down your target. This makes sure that your target will be chased away or will be zoned out from the team fight making the target useless. Aside from the crowd control, this deals enough amount of damage to make the enemy fall back. Make sure that you are going punish your target with this ability.",
